title: Pearl Jam - Discography
description:
Hi guys, I'm uploading Pearl Jam's discography with their latest album "Lightning Bolt", thats why I'm doing this upload because all previous discographys are outdated. 

It contains all studio albums:

Ten, Versus, 
Vitalogy, 
No code, 
Yield, 
Live on two legs, 
Binaural, 
Rioct Act, 
Backspacer,
Lightning Bolt, 
MTV unplugged.

The files are in mp3 format, all the albums have their covers, hope you like it and seed for how long you want!
Please visit this thread for more info: https://forum.suprbay.org/showthread.php?tid=154990&pid=904028#pid904028
